**FR-01-Card Selection**

**Description** → The application shall provide a graphical user interface that allows the player to select a single card from their current hand and play it onto the game board during their designated turn in each round.

**Main Stage →** The user´s turn will start and the will need to choose a card to play. Once he chooses it, he plays it and his turn ends

**Pre conditions →** The user has started a game

**Post conditions →** The user´s turn will have finished

**Exceptions** → until the user doesn´t choose a card, the game won´t be able to continue, when the turn´s countdown reaches 0, the current user´s turn will finish and he will loose his turn.

